abstract: Occupy Wall Street protesters in Zuccotti Park sought to eliminate the need for a planned cleaning by the city on Friday.
snippet: Occupy Wall Street protesters in Zuccotti Park sought to eliminate the need for a planned cleaning by the city on Friday.
lead_paragraph: Updated, 9:21 p.m.| Young people in knit hats and jeans scurried around Thursday wielding brooms and trash bags, moving mountains of sleeping bags, backpacks and jackets out of the way.

headline.main: Facing Eviction, Protesters Begin Park Cleanup
